N">Ganges</ENAMEX>. The <ENAMEX TYPE="PRODUCT_DESC">river</ENAMEX> is also where on many occasions during <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the year</TIMEX> the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">faithful</ENAMEX> take ritual purification <ENAMEX TYPE="FAC_DESC">baths</ENAMEX>.
