X TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> look on this as a staging point for a trek, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Pokhara</ENAMEX> is such a beautiful spot that it can be quite enough just to relax and enjoy the mountain scenery in the warm sunshine.
